name: One Eye Open Issue #1
description:
This magazine hopes to provide a range of articles loosely centred around music, film and culture. It hopes to bring to light music that you may not have heard, films that you may not have watched and subjects that you may not have thought about. But it does not matter if you have listened to, watched or thought about these things before - the most important thing is that whatever is being written about, means a great deal to the writer.

Issue #1: Happiness, Villagers, Mona, Xuuki, New Sounds, Alice Gold, Million Dead, Alessi's Ark, Pick Me Up.
